 Barry Diller


 
Producer





Barry Diller was born on February 2, 1942 in San Francisco, California, USA as Barry Charles Diller. He is a producer, known for Top Five (2014), Everything Is Copy (2015) and AFI Life Achievement Award: A Tribute to Warren Beatty (2008).            
See full bio »
            
 


Born:

February 2, 
     
1942

            in
            San Francisco, California, USA





